values:
Alrighty!&nbsp; I'm all moved!&nbsp; I took Thursday and Friday off.&nbsp; On Thursday we did a bunch of running around and we checked on highschools for Andrew.&nbsp; We also changed the U-Haul reservations from Saturday to Friday.&nbsp; Got up early friday morning and it took 2 trips to get it all together.&nbsp; I didnt know I had this much crap.&nbsp; Sigh.&nbsp; Unpacked pretty much all of friday night and saturday.&nbsp; Almost done with it all.&nbsp; So tomorrow I'm gonna take it a bit easy and chill.&nbsp; I'm sore as shit since it was just me, Billy, Billy's friend James, Andrew and his friend Deandre.&nbsp; I didn't have to drive the truck, another one of Billy's friends did that.&nbsp; He couldnt help us load or unload but he drove it for me.&nbsp; 
I'm sore as shit and tired as hell but ABSOLUTLY LOVE LOVE LOVE my new house.&nbsp; It's so nice.&nbsp; I'll take some pictures once I'm all settled in.&nbsp; 
I didn't realize how much the old house depressed me.&nbsp; It was so dark and dusty and I don't care how much I cleaned it never looked clean.&nbsp; This house here is light and airy.&nbsp; I have celing fans in every room and the floors are soooooooooooooooo nice.&nbsp; 

here is my new Adress for you guys:&nbsp;&nbsp; 3835 Travis Blvd.&nbsp; Macon GA 31206

I'm taking my tired ass to bed now!!&nbsp; Luves ya!!

So Billy is all squared away now I can concentrate on Andrew.&nbsp; He didnt make it again this year and has to go to summer school again.&nbsp; Sigh....
$400.00 for 2 classes!&nbsp; I&nbsp;found out last wednesday and just didnt want to let it take away from Billy's success.&nbsp; So I called his Dad to tell him and also let him know that the kids can't come to spend the summer with him because of it.&nbsp; At first he was ok with it and agreed to pay half of it.&nbsp; I told him&nbsp;I would call him back when I knew the details.&nbsp; 

So I found out the details and called him back and first thing he asks if I had already paid.&nbsp; I said no because registration is next Monday.&nbsp; Then he tells me that he is not paying because Andrew needs to learn a lesson and take responsibility.&nbsp; He also went off on&nbsp; me for not having him tested for ADD.&nbsp; I&nbsp;just didnt have the time to get all that done.&nbsp; 
Anyways...Andrew can't repeat another class because he will be to old to graduate....so I guess I'm gonna have to pay the whole $400 alone...asshole.&nbsp; But Andrew is going...next year he will be out of this school system and hopefully with Teachers that care.&nbsp; I&nbsp;also already made an appointment for him to start the testing process.&nbsp; 
I could take the ex back to court but its gonna cost me a lot more to get that done, than what I would get.&nbsp; 

The next 2 month are gonna be hell....bleh...with Andrew going to summerschool, Billy going to college, Us moving...omg...I'm getting tired just reading this...

Have a great Sunday!
